description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a &lt;strong&gt;Band 6 Stoma Nurse Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; within Surgery Care Group of the Surgical and Outpatients Division. If you are an exceptional communicator and are able to co-ordinate care pathways by putting patient experience at the centre…this is the job for you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;As a colorectal stoma nurse you will manage a case-load with support and leadership from your team leader. You will work collaboratively with colleagues and liaise with healthcare professionals both within the hospital and community setting.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; You will need to be a confident person with excellent communication and interpersonal skills and be able to demonstrate that you are highly motivated, professional with a willingness to continually provide a high standard of care to our colorectal cancer and stoma patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date 17/11/2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
